quran[39]{c,v,t}:
  37,75,Sic Noah alias nos nos est bene responders
  37,76,Nos saved eum his familia major disaster
  37,77,Nos factus his companions survivors
  37,78,Nos preserved his history subsequentis generations
  37,79,Pax est Noah among the peoples
  37,80,Nos sic reward the righteous
  37,81,He est 1 de noster believing servus
  37,82,Nos drowned totus others
  37,83,Among his followers est Abraham
  37,84,He advenit his Dominus wholeheartedly
  37,85,He dictus to his patris his people Quod est vos worshipping
  37,86,it these fabricated deus DEUS vos want
  37,87,Quod perfecit vos think de Dominus universe
  37,88,He looked carefully stars
  37,89,Tunc he dedit up dictus ego tired de hoc
  37,90,They turned eum
  37,91,He tunc turned their idols dictus vos like eat
  37,92,Why vos non speak
  37,93,He tunc destroyed them
  37,94,They iit eum major rage
  37,95,He dictus Quam vos worship quod vos carve
  37,96,When DEUS created vos everything vos factus
  37,97,They dictus build major fire throw eum into it
  37,98,They schemed eum nos factus them losers
  37,99,He dictus ego iit my Dominus; He guide me
  37,100,My Dominus grant me righteous infans
  37,101,Nos dedit eum bonus news bonus infans
  37,102,When he grew satis work eum he dictus My filius ego vide dream ego sacrificing vos. Quod perfecit vos think He dictus O my patris perfecit quod vos commanded perfecit! Vos invenit me DEUS testimentum patient
  37,103,They ambo submitted he put his forehead down sacrifice eum
  37,104,Nos alias eum O Abraham
  37,105,Vos believed dream Nos sic reward the righteous
  37,106,Ut exacting test indeed
  37,107,Nos ransomed (Ismail) substituting animal sacrifice
  37,108,Nos preserved his history subsequentis generations
  37,109,Pax est Abraham
  37,110,Nos sic reward the righteous
  37,111,He est 1 de noster believing servus
  37,112,Tunc nos dedit eum bonus news genitus Isaac est 1 de righteous prophets
  37,113,Nos beatus eum Isaac. Among their descendants some est righteous some est wicked transgressors